# Medimate â€“ Your Smart Health Assistant

Medimate is a wellness-focused web application designed to help users stay on top of their health. It provides personalized reminders, hydration tracking, diet tips, and interactive features to make health management engaging and effortless.

## ðŸš€ Project Overview

Medimate is a *medication and wellness reminder* website that supports users in:
- Keeping track of medicine intake.
- Getting regular hydration alerts.
- Accessing smart diet tips.
- Enjoying health-based games.
- Viewing personalized wellness analysis.

The goal is to *combine healthcare with interactivity* to promote a healthy lifestyle through timely notifications and user-friendly interfaces.

