> Note: The current version is run locally (index.html) and does not yet include backend integration.

## âœ¨ Features

- *Medication Reminders*: Set alerts to take your medicine on time.
- *Hydration Tracker*: Stay hydrated with regular water intake notifications.
- *Smart Diet Tips*: Get personalized tips for a balanced diet.
- *Interactive Games*: Health-themed games for engagement and education.
- *Report Analysis*: Track your progress and health stats (planned feature).
- *User-friendly Interface*: Clean, responsive design with easy navigation.

